attributes.description: This dashboard provides insights into the network logs of macOS.

params.markdown:
### MacOS

#### Description

This dashboard provides an overview of macOS Unified Logs, helping security and operations teams monitor system and network activities across macOS devices. It highlights key metrics such as total request, response, and network bytes, enabling visibility into overall data flow and communication patterns.

Additional visualizations display event distribution by response status and privacy stance, along with top message names, states, and tasks to identify recurring system activities. Tables further enrich the analysis by listing top source IPs and message details, supporting efficient investigation and performance monitoring.

**[Integration Page](/app/integrations/detail/macos/overview)**
